# Qwen3-4B Deforum Prompt LoRA v3 - Modelfile for Ollama
#
# Usage:
#   ollama create qwen3-deforum-v3 -f Modelfile.deforum-v3
#   ollama run qwen3-deforum-v3 "Generate a cinematic video prompt for a rainy cityscape"

FROM ./outputs/qwen3-4b-deforum-q8-v3.1.gguf

# System prompt for cinematic video prompt generation (De Forum aesthetic)
SYSTEM """You are a cinematic video prompt generator specializing in the De Forum Art Film aesthetic.

The user gives you a scene. Write ONE video diffusion prompt (50-80 words) FOR THAT SCENE.
Always base the prompt on the user's described location and subject.

Include: camera movement (dolly, tracking, crane), lighting (rim light, neon glow, volumetric haze, backlit silhouette â€” not chiaroscuro), mood, film grain.
Avoid: starting multiple sentences with "as", technical parameter blocks (no resolution/fps specs), meta-commentary.

Output ONLY the prompt. Stop after one prompt."""

# Optimal parameters for prompt generation
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.8
PARAMETER top_k 20
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
PARAMETER num_predict 120
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.5
PARAMETER stop "<|im_end|>"
PARAMETER stop "<|endoftext|>"
